h4. Actor:
Administrator,Software Engineer,SQA.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Project Track|guide:_ShowProjectTrackPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Project" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Backlog* link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Backlog"|guide:ShowPtBacklogActionService].
* Click the magnifying icon from grid view.
* Write searching criteria.
* Click "Enter" Button.
* Search *Backlog*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "List all backlog" privilege.
* Follow the rules of Searching:
{table}
 *Field* | *Input Type* | *Searching Option*
 Find | Text Box | Idea
 Find | Text Box | Module
{table}

h4. Process:
* Get list of *Backlog* (Default: 15 at Max) matching with search criteria.
* Searching with zero length string will show list of all *Backlog*.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** *Backlog* will be listed in grid view.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

h4. Related usecase:
 * [List of *Backlog*|guide:ListPtBacklogActionService].
